  <item>Men who have sex with men (MSM) are also identified as high risk.</item></list></entry>
  <entry valign="top" align="left"><list list-type="bulleted" id="list-00064"><item>Vaccination for all adults under age 60, but anyone may request it and receive it.</item>
  <item>Universal screening at least once in the lifetime of all adults, and more often with ongoing risk factors such as pregnancy, hepatitis C infection, and individuals who are incarcerated, have a history of sexually transmitted infections, or have multiple sexual partners.</item></list></entry>
